creator: Mary Mollineux
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of On the Sight of a Skull by Mary Mollineux. This was the Weekly Poetry project for March 29, 2015. Read in English by Annalyn; Aaron Walsh; Bruce Kachuk; David Lawrence; Elise C. Boucher; Garth Burton; Greg Giordano; J. McDougall; Lee Ann Howlett and Larry Wilson. This poem is taken from A Book of Women’s Verse published in 1921. ( David Lawrence) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
